NAME Quick Terminal Recon
DESCRIPTION Opens a terminal on any OS and runs a command
CATEGORY recon
PLATFORMS WIN,MAC,LINUX
OPTION COMMAND whoami "Command to execute"
OPTION DELAY 2000 "Initial HID delay (ms)"
PLATFORM ALL
DELAY {{DELAY}}
LED_COLOR BLUE
OPEN_TERMINAL
STRINGLN {{COMMAND}}
DELAY 1000
LED_COLOR GREEN
